      "biography": {
        "value": "<p><em>Greeting: \"The frigid veil persists.\" | Response: \"All the world in winter's white.\" | Parting: \"May her blessing chill you.\"</em></p><p>Darkhands recruit and train new members, ruling the rank-and-file with pitiless demeanor. They receive a ring of black ice engraved with Auril's symbol \u2014 a dark badge of authority. Each darkhand manages two tempests and oversees six to eight spites. Boon of Frost (+4 CON/STR) included in statblock.</p><p><strong>Renown 10 | CR 2</strong></p>"
